snippet.title: Why Jim and Amber Marchese Were Fired from RHONJ; Tried to Sue NBC | #NoFilter
snippet.description:
Former Bravo star Amber Marchese is dishing on her time on the Real Housewives of New Jersey, claiming her husband Jim Marchese's threats to sue NBC solidified their firing on the show. Catch the full interview now: https://apple.co/341uSa0

Listen to the #NoFilter Podcast: https://apple.co/35rqH6u
